summary: About $LOG - $LOG is the pioneering meme coin introducing Land Dog, the confident social media alter ego of Landwolf. $WOLF and $LOG are the only officially named Landwolf coins featured in the comic. In the Boys Club comic, on page 143, Landwolf appears as "land_dog," taking a bathroom mirror selfie. He embodies more than just a meme; he represents a confident and iconic lifestyle, supported by his friends Andyman, Brettness, Young Peezy, and his community.
